  "body_html": "<p>Fragrance Notes:<br>Top Notes: Rosemary, Coconut Water, Sea Breeze Accord<br>Heart Notes: Tiare Flower, Ylang-Ylang, Jasmine<br>Base Notes: Vanilla, White Musk, Driftwood<br>The Vibe:<br>Tan line is like a tropical escape in every spray—fresh, creamy, and sun-drenched. It opens with refreshing coconut water and salty sea air, then melts into soft white florals that feel like skin warmed by the sun. The vanilla and musk in the base give it a smooth, comforting finish. It's the perfect scent for beach days, summer nights, or anytime you want to feel like you're on vacation. Carefree, breezy, and glow-giving.</p>",
